9 §201-E Community and cultural partnership program;
10 established. (a) In addition to other duties, the office shall
11 establish a community and cultural partnership program focused
12 on improving communities. The program shall serve as a
13 community resource to enhance historical culture, stimulate
14 social and economic activity, create positive change in the
15 community, and serve as a template for improvements in other
16 communities, as may be appropriate.
17 (b) The office may contract with one or more entities to
18 administer the community and cultural partnership program and
19 complete the actions required by subsection (c).
20 (c) The program shall endeavor to:
