13 who are considering property improvements to best
14 reflect the cultural narrative and historical context
15 of the area;
16 (5) Organize culture and arts and improvement projects to
17 improve and expand public spaces and enhance streets,
18 infrastructure, facades, and vacant storefronts;
19 (6) Organize community culture and arts events, including
20 the closures of streets for events and multi-use
21 purposes that can enhance community life by providing
