6 SECTION 3. There is appropriated out of the general
7 revenues of the State of Hawaii the sum of $300,000 or so much
8 thereof as may be necessary for fiscal year 2026-2027 for the
9 establishment of the office of community culture, arts, and
10 innovation, including for the following purposes:
11 (1) The establishment of one full-time equivalent
12 (1.0 FTE) executive director position;
13 (2) The establishment of one full-time equivalent
14 (1.0 FTE) specialist position; and
15 (3) Other expenses for the purposes of this Act.
16 The sum appropriated shall be expended by the department of
17 business, economic development, and tourism for the purposes of
18 this Act.
19 SECTION 4. In codifying the new sections added by
20 section 2 of this Act, the revisor of statutes shall substitute
